snippet.title: Whispering Hills | A Fallout 4 Mod | Trailer
snippet.description:
Whispering Hills is a Silent Hill overhaul mod for Fallout developed by Team Whisper.

Download Whispering Hills on:
Nexus: https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mo...​
ModDb: https://www.moddb.com/mods/whispering...

Made this trailer as another little quick editing activity for myself so I hope everyone enjoys the trailer and supports the mod!
